A Sharia Court sitting in Magajin Gari in Kaduna State, on Tuesday, sentenced a teenage student, Anas Sidi-Baba, to one-year imprisonment over sexual encroachment on, and criminal intimidation of, his stepmother. The News Agency of Nigeria (NAN) reported that after the defendant had pleaded guilty of the offence, he told the court that he was enchanted by his stepbrothers. Sidi Baba said: “My step-brothers enchanted me and made me become a drug addict. Sometimes, I go naked and sometimes, I do wake up late at night to pray.” The judge, Murtala Nasir, however, granted the convict a bail option of N20,000, and that he must also pay N20,000 as compensation to the complainant. 57-year-old man allegedly rapes 8-year-old girl in Ekiti Police arraign teenager over alleged burglary, stealing Teenager allegedly steals NRC electric cables worth N3.1m Teenager allegedly shoots man dead with local gun ALSO READ: Security guard allegedly rapes 9 year old Earlier, the police counsel, Sergeant Aliyu Ibrahim, told the court that on December 5, at about 6.00 pm., one Fatima Sidi-Baba of Unguan Sanusi, Kaduna, reported the incident to the Metro police division. The council said that Sidi-Baba went into her room while she was asleep and that most times, he would come in naked. “On December 3, at about 2.30 a.m., she saw him while using his cell phone’s torch to peep into her window. She came out and held him, while the phone and a stick of cigarette fell off his hands,” he said. Ibrahim, who said that the offence was punishable under Section 232 of Sharia Penal Code, prayed the court to sanction Sidi-Baba accordingly, while also ordering him to pay N20,000 as compensation for the fear he instilled in his stepmother. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE
